title: Locomotives International - April/May 2016
description:
English | 68 pages | PDF | 72.7 MB

Locomotives International is a high quality bi-monthly publication, and is the only UK-based magazine devoted to railways around the world. The title has recently expanded following the integration into its pages of the "Continental Railway Journal", and it continues to grow and develop with each issue. All issues contain a mixture of colour and black and white images, which supplement the well researched articles and news items
